@prefix : <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/pe#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix xml: <http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@base <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/pe#> .

<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/pe> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                         owl:imports <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox> ;
                                         :profilingPolicy """
Programming-language profiling uses only native support and standard-library support.
Refined concepts are asserted selectively rather than exhaustively.
No support is recorded for mere encodings or otherwise insignificant realizations.
Refined support is not inherited automatically from coarse support.
Support assertions are qualified only when especially representative or potentially ambiguous.
Borderline cases may be documented using skos:note.
Paradigm-based subclassing of programming languages is not used; paradigms are represented via concept support.
"""@en ;
                                         <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#commentingPolicy> "See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here."@en ;
                                         <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#formattingPolicy> "See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here."@en ;
                                         <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#linkingPolicy> "See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here."@en ;
                                         <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#metamodelingPolicy> "See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here."@en ;
                                         rdfs:comment "Sub-ontology / ABox for programming-language concepts and programming languages"@en .

#################################################################
#    Annotation properties
#################################################################

###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/pe#profilingPolicy
:profilingPolicy rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#assertedForConcept
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#assertedForConcept> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


