###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#hasSpace
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#hasSpace> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#hasSupportKind
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#hasSupportKind> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#linkingPolicy
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#linkingPolicy> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#metamodelingPolicy
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#metamodelingPolicy> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#nativelySupports
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#nativelySupports> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#standardlySupports
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#standardlySupports> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note
<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopicOf
<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopicOf> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page
<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


#################################################################
#    Classes
#################################################################

###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/pe#ProgrammingLanguage
:ProgrammingLanguage rdf:type owl:Class ;
                     rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#SoftwareLanguage> .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageEntity
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageEntity> rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageSupportAssertion
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageSupportAssertion> rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#SoftwareLanguage
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#SoftwareLanguage> rdf:type owl:Class .


